ESMT said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 19.99% to NT$426,010,000 from NT$532,426,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales            426,010          532,426    
YOY%             -19.99%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           2,191,558        2,827,121   
YOY%             -22.48% 
=================================================================
 